body_html: @jbobba Could you re-open this? The Eigen patch ( https://bitbucket.org/eigen/eigen/pull-requests/407/fix-the-packet16h-version-of-ptranspose/diff ) that fixes the issue hasn't been merged into Eigen yet and so is not included in the recent tensorflow Eigen update. We need to get the patch merged and then do another Eigen update before this issue can be closed.
